      "title": "## Overview",
      "content": "This plan outlines a modern, forward-looking website for OAMx (Ohio Advanced Mobility Exchange). It will showcase past and future events, provide detailed information about the 2025 event, facilitate involvement from students, professionals, and partners, and include dedicated sections for team members and contact information."
    },
    {
      "id": "key-features",
      "title": "## Key features",
      "content": "- **View Homepage Content**: Displays introductory information about OAMx, its mission, and highlights.\n- **View About Information**: Provides details on OAMx's evolution from the Ohio UAM Symposium and its forward-looking identity.\n- **View Event Listing**: Showcases a list of past and future OAMx events.\n- **Filter Events**: Allows users to filter events by type (past/future) or category.\n- **View Event Details**: Displays comprehensive information for a specific event, including theme, schedule, and sponsorship opportunities.\n- **View 2025 Event Information**: Presents specific details for the upcoming 2025 event.\n- **View 2025 Event Schedule**: Lists the schedule of sessions and activities for the 2025 event.\n- **Submit Registration Form**: Allows visitors to register for events, particularly the 2025 event.\n- **View Get Involved Information**: Outlines clear pathways for students, industry professionals, and partners to participate.\n- **View Team Listing**: Displays a list of OAMx team members.\n- **View Team Member Details**: Shows detailed profiles for individual team members.\n- **Submit Contact Form**: Enables visitors to send inquiries to OAMx.\n- **View Press/Media Kit**: Provides access to a downloadable press and media kit.\n- **Subscribe to Newsletter**: Allows users to sign up for email updates."
    },
    {
      "id": "structure",
