      "content": "- **Homepage**: Serves as the main entry point, featuring an overview of OAMx and key highlights.\n- **About Page**: Details OAMx's mission, history, and innovative identity.\n- **2025 Event Page**: Dedicated section for the upcoming event, including theme, schedule, and sponsorship details.\n- **Get Involved Page**: Information on how different groups can participate.\n- **Registration & Ticketing Page**: Hosts the event registration forms.\n- **Mentorship Program Page**: Information about the upcoming mentorship program.\n- **Meet the Team Page**: Displays the OAMx team members.\n- **Press/Media Kit Page**: Offers downloadable resources for media."
